data.description: Phillips Ranch! The perfect commuter location where FWY 60 & FWY 71 meet; also providing quick access to FWY 10 & 57.  A stately parkway entrance sets the stage as you drive into the lovely community of Phillips Meadows. This home is a 2nd story unit, enhanced by gorgeous NEW (installed 2021) double-pane windows & sliding door! Enjoy an open concept living area with a real wood-burning fireplace, exposed beams on a vaulted ceiling and smooth slider access to your private balcony. At one end of the balcony is the laundry niche w/double door access; no need for “stackable” appliances here, this area is big enough for standard sized washer & dryer – and the electric dryer is included in the sale!  The family chef will enjoy preparing meals with the brand new electric range which includes an “Air-fryer” feature!  Go ahead, use as many pots & pans as you like, there’s a dishwasher to take care of the cleanup. Beautiful engineered wood flooring, carpeting in all three bedrooms, tile flooring in both bathrooms. The master suite with extra large picture windows offers plenty of wardrobe storage, a nice vanity with granite countertop, walk-in shower, and the commode is in a separate space w/privacy door.  The two secondary bedrooms shine with ample natural lighting (oh, those lovely new windows!) These bedrooms share a hall bathroom where it’s much easier to bathe the little ones in the shower-tub combo.  An oversized loft (approx. 19' X 9') with big sky lite creates the perfect private office space, library/study, workout room, kid’s playroom, or even a potential 4th bedroom; the loft provides access to attic space that could be converted to a closet, use it for storage or? HOA dues include landscape & exterior building maintenance, community pool, spas, greenbelts, picnic area, security patrol & “on demand” hot water to the units.  Detached garage is right in front of the unit, one-car garage space #118 (it's a two-car garage shared with a neighbor) plus one assigned open parking space. Guest permit parking available. Approx. 1,323 Sq.Ft. per tax roll, not taped, Buyer(s) to verify. *It’s a quick commute to Cal Poly Pomona approx. 4.3 miles. This location is a shopper's paradise! *Both Winco & Walmart are less than ½ mile away, Rolling Ridge Plaza/99 Ranch Mkt, Costco approx. 2.7 miles! The Shoppes at Chino Hills only 3.5 miles via Peyton Dr.
